                        "TILA section 129C(b)(2)(vi) states that the term qualified mortgage includes any mortgage loan \u201cthat complies with any guidelines or regulations established by the Bureau relating to ratios of total monthly debt to monthly income or alternative measure of ability to pay regular expenses after payment of total monthly debt, taking into account the income levels of the consumer and such other factors as the Bureau may determine relevant and consistent with the purposes described in paragraph (3)(B)(i).\u201d"
