                        "Proposed \u00a7 226.43(a)(3)(i) created an exemption from the ability-to-repay requirements in \u00a7 226.43(c) through (f) for reverse mortgages, as provided in the statute. The Bureau did not receive comments on this exemption.\n            Accordingly, the Bureau is adopting \u00a7 1026.43(a)(3)(i) as proposed."
